{"tid":2267893,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"華為：已掌握 200W 無線快充技術","createTime":"2020-11-02T11:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T07:24:24.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"64c51d41ada866f68c7c613bea5bcc7d32ae3073","tid":2267893,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"華為早前在發布&nbsp;Mate40 Pro 和 Pro+ 時，表示其實已經掌握到 120W，甚至是 200W 的無線充電技術，但就未有在 Mate 40系列上使用，是因為高達 200W 的快充更適合容量大的電池。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n華為在本月 30 日於上海東方體育中心舉行年度旗艦新品發布盛典，華為消費者業務 CEO 余承東在發布上介紹此次發布的 Mate40 Pro 和 Pro+，指系列手機配備 66W 有線快充以及 50W 無線快充，而其補充，華為其實已經掌握到 120W，甚至是 200W 的無線充電技術，不採用只是不想犧牲電池的容量以及安全性。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n余承東表示，高達 200W 的快充更適合容量大的電池，如果要套用 Mate 40 系列就要犧牲其電池容量。同時，他表示對於目前的智能電話而言，過度充電的穩定性不足，如果使用 200W 的快充有可能會不安全。"},{"pid":"fa7c6e74f62f49506a245a797a0ebd1900715bdb","tid":2267893,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f098fe40c5c2985896f4005654c68681463b625c","tid":2267893,"uid":704,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:39:41.000Z","msg":"我掌握100000W無線快充技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a11cffdf75ac76026fd5c9ecfe9327bb9a0cb55","tid":2267893,"uid":65743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzLhFPq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzLhFPq.gif&h=2150b165&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc1d8269d2a3d29993c85155d77c645f62ecd897","tid":2267893,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a11cffdf75ac76026fd5c9ecfe9327bb9a0cb55","tid":2267893,"uid":65743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kzLhFPq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkzLhFPq.gif&h=2